<Layout title="Community" description="Links and contribution info for Wasteland Front — Last War: Survival guides.">
  <h1>Community</h1>
  <p>This site exists because the Last War community shares knowledge freely on Reddit and in alliances.</p>

  <h2>Recommended Places</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://reddit.com/r/LastWarMobileGame" target="_blank" rel="noopener">r/LastWarMobileGame</a> — Active discussion and guide sharing</li>
    <li>Your alliance Discord / in-game chat — the fastest source of server-specific meta</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contributing</h2>
  <p>Found an error, better strategy, or want to suggest a new page? The repo is public: <a href="https://github.com/cblack34/wastelandfront" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/cblack34/wastelandfront</a>.</p>
  <p class="text-sm text-[#5e6b85] mt-2">All content is written for new and mid-game players first. Accuracy and scannability matter more than volume.</p>

  <h2>Other Good Resources</h2>
  <ul class="text-sm">
    <li>Active alliance Discords — best for real-time server meta</li>
    <li>Seasonal hero guides from top players on Reddit (search for Aethernis-style guides)</li>
    <li>In-game Wall of Honor and alliance chat for practical testing results</li>
  </ul>
</Layout>